  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的流程图，核心是课堂服务（ClassroomService）和内容分发网络（ContentCDN）之间的交互逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那ContentCDN是一个判断节点吗？比如检查资源是否可用？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ContentCDN是第一个决策点。如果资源可用（Yes），就进入LMS门户；如果不可用（No），要回到ClassroomService重新请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主流程画出来：ClassroomService指向ContentCDN判断节点，然后分出Yes/No两条分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "LMS门户那边也需要判断，用户是否通过身份验证。通过的话，还要再检查一次ContentCDN的最终资源状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以LMS Portal也是一个菱形判断节点？Yes分支继续往下，No分支呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "No分支直接连到ContentCDN的一个终止节点，表示流程结束但标记为失败状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了LMS Portal的分支。现在Yes分支指向第二个ContentCDN判断，确认最终资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这个最终ContentCDN判断很关键：如果资源最终可用，进入成绩同步服务GradeSync；如果还是不行，也进GradeSync但标记不同状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到。所以第二个ContentCDN分出两条线，都到GradeSync，但后续处理不同对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，成功的GradeSync要再连回ContentCDN做最终确认；失败的GradeSync直接汇总到结束节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加GradeSync节点和它的两条出边。现在处理汇聚：之前ContentCDN的No分支、LMS Portal的No分支、还有失败的GradeSync，这三条都要汇总到一起。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，第一个ContentCDN的No分支应该是回到ClassroomService重新请求，不是直接结束。我刚才可能没说清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "明白，我修正一下。第一个ContentCDN的No分支改为指向ClassroomService，形成循环。然后这个ClassroomService再连到汇聚节点I。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这样逻辑就通了。汇聚节点I代表所有异常或完成流程的终点。最后成功的GradeSync要连到ContentCDN节点J做最终归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "流程结构完成了。现在需要区分成功和失败路径的视觉样式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。成功的GradeSync节点用绿色填充；所有失败路径上的节点——包括循环回的ClassroomService、LMS Portal的No分支终点、以及失败的GradeSync——都用红色填充。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：绿色的是G节点（成功的GradeSync）；红色的是D节点（循环的ClassroomService）、F节点（LMS Portal的No分支）、H节点（失败的GradeSync）。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。文字都用白色，确保对比度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式已应用。整个流程图现在清晰展示了：从ClassroomService出发，经过ContentCDN和LMS Portal的多层判断，最终根据资源可用性分别进入成功或失败的GradeSync处理，并汇聚到统一终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
